{
  "stem": "3658.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So one day, my father was-- we were standing all in rows, and he and half the group that was standing in the row was taken to what you called the Sonderkommando.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 8 SECONDS] [SOBBING] [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so he was taken there to work.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So he says to me, how much bread have you got?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[SOBBING] He took his last piece of bread and gave me his.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[CRYING] So that was upsetting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[SOBBING] That's the last I saw him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I was told that they-- they were supposed to-- to-- to sort of, burn their own people, you know?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I heard that they blew up the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what I've heard.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know how true that is, but I've heard that they [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I've never seen him again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He never came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was just-- he left in the morning for work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And normally, they-- they come back.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So it must've been true, because he never came back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was on my own.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then they took the-- the worst thing hurt me, that I took his piece of bread in the morning when he left.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] That stays with me.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, he said, you-- I've got some.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, you won't have enough for today.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, and I'll see when I come back.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now, we're going to work.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We kissed, and that was that.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [SIGHS] [CRYING] I stayed in Auschwitz for a few days.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then, they were taking-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then, they were taking different blocks to go to different camps.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they asked our block to-- to [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That means to-- to-- to stand.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
